Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Brave Browser Debloater - UNDO
; Removes ALL managed policies set by debloat-brave-windows.reg
;
; This deletes the entire Brave policy key, which removes every
; policy value under it in one step.
;
; Usage:
;   1. Close Brave completely
;   2. Double-click this .reg file
;   3. Click "Yes" on confirmation prompts
;   4. Restart Brave and visit brave://policy to verify

[-HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\BraveSoftware\Brave]